request.description:
> [../../_.py](../../../../_.py#L6)

A hello world


### Authentication

There is no authentication rule defined

### Response

#### Example response

```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Successfully processed your request",
    "error": null,
    "data": {
        "hello": "no example",
        "hi": "no example"
    }
}

```

#### Returns

| Field        | Description                      | Type   | Nullable  |
| ----------   | -------------------------------- | ------ | --------- |
| `hello` | No description  | <class 'str'>      | No      |
| `hi` | No description  | <class 'str'>      | No      |
